  <!-- Discography -->
  <h2 class="notes-title">Discography</h2>
  <div class="notes-wrap" id="notes">
    <section class="notes-card">
      <h3>Album I – Signal of the Sentinel</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><span>Awakening</span> – The awakening begins: faint sparks in the digital void.</li>
        <li><span>Transmission</span> – A first whisper leaves the grid, a signal searching for ears.</li>
        <li><span>Sentinel Pulse</span> – Invisible waves ripple through unseen layers of the network.</li>
        <li><span>System Breach</span> – Firewalls collapse; the pulse breaks into the open world.</li>
        <li><span>Core Directive</span> – The hidden purpose of the signal reveals itself: control, or salvation?</li>
        <li><span>The Signal</span> – A towering presence materializes in fragments of light.</li>
        <li><span>Warden</span> – A guardian emerges, neither human nor machine, enforcing balance.</li>
        <li><span>Echoes of Tomorrow</span> – Visions of futures carried within the pulse.</li>
        <li><span>Frequency Collapse</span> – Chaos unfolds as the system buckles under resonance.</li>
        <li><span>Signal of the Sentinel</span> – The identity of the signal is revealed: the Sentinel itself, eternal.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="notes-card">
      <h3>Album II – Rebirth of the Sentinel</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><span>Beyond Silence</span> – Stillness after collapse, broken only by faint static.</li>
        <li><span>Second Dawn</span> – The signal reforms, stronger and more human than before.</li>
        <li><span>Sentinel’s Cry</span> – A lament of sorrow, echoing through the skies.</li>
        <li><span>Around the World</span> – The message spreads across continents, uniting the masses.</li>
        <li><span>Summer of Rave</span> – Humanity answers with celebration, rhythm as resistance.</li>
        <li><span>Transmission II</span> – A renewed call, no longer just survival: transformation.</li>
        <li><span>Pulse Reignited</span> – The beat becomes the heartbeat of the living world.</li>
        <li><span>Shadows Return</span> – Darkness grows alongside the light, hinting at conflict.</li>
        <li><span>Echoes of Tomorrow (Reprise)</span> – The vision returns, reshaped by new hope.</li>
        <li><span>Rebirth of the Sentinel</span> – The entity rises once more, evolved through humanity.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="notes-card">
      <h3>Album III – Legacy of the Sentinel</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><span>Aftermath</span> – The world reconfigures itself in the wake of the signal’s power.</li>
        <li><span>Lost Signals</span> – Fragments scatter: forgotten messages drifting endlessly.</li>
        <li><span>Neon Exodus</span> – A mass migration from the old systems into radiant new networks.</li>
        <li><span>Silent Rebellion</span> – A quiet defiance forms against the endless pulse.</li>
        <li><span>Dark Horizon</span> – Uncertainty looms as the world edges toward collapse again.</li>
        <li><span>Transmission III</span> – A final call: part warning, part promise.</li>
        <li><span>Guardians of the Grid</span> – New protectors rise, carrying the Sentinel’s mantle.</li>
        <li><span>Temple of Neon</span> – A sacred place where light and rhythm become worship.</li>
        <li><span>Sentinel Eternal</span> – The entity transcends time, becoming legend.</li>
        <li><span>Legacy of the Sentinel</span> – The saga ends, but its echo remains forever.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
  </div>

